[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Will [bold]the proposal [bold]save money?[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]“It may be saving the Legal Services Commission which no longer offers legal aid for this k
[normal]ind of litigation  but saving expenditure in one public department in this instance simply increases it in the courts. The expense of three judges of the Court of Appeal dealing with this kind of appeal is enormous. The consequences by way of delay  of oth
[normal]er appeals which 
[normal]need to
[normal] be heard are unquantifiable. The appeal would certainly never have occurred if the litigants had been represented.”
